{"tid":1849761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(未FC/半FC) 八間預定流感診所(隔離站)位置周邊住宅/中小學幼稚園/商場","createTime":"2020-01-29T08:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T09:53:01.000Z","uid":69416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0f08e4af19c4b4cccae64c621b81226787230f98","tid":1849761,"uid":69416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:17:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1846321/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1846321/page/1</a><br />\nQuote番琴日個Post<br />\n由於九龍灣果間似乎已經FC，而屯門亦有區議員展開聯署抗議<br />\n因此小弟就決定仔細望下哩八間診所既位置同周邊環境<br />\n懶人包：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 每個隔離站幾乎完全被密集住宅包圍</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2a. 幾乎每個隔離站附近100米範圍內必定有中小學幼稚園</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">  b. 每個隔離站一公里範圍內必定有中小學幼稚園</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">  c. 每個隔離站一公里範圍內平均有3-5間中小學幼稚園</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. (個人推測) 屌你老母臭閪港共政府想透過武漢肺炎大量虐殺香港本土居民</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n以下係各個診所既地圖<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">紅色 : 隔離所</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">橙色 : 住宅用地</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">綠色 : 中小學幼稚園</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍色 : 商場/人流高度密集場所</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由於係靠肉眼觀察因此可能會有另漏 麻煩當區巴打再補充</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">九龍灣：九龍灣健康中心普通科門診診所</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">住宅：<br />\n　麗晶花園／啟泰苑／德朗邨</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">中小學幼稚園：<br />\n　聖公會九龍灣基樂小學<br />\n　基督教小天使(麗晶)幼稚園<br />\n　天主教柏德學校<br />\n　仁濟醫院羅陳楚思小學</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">高機會人流密集處：<br />\n　啟業商場</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iKNsfEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiKNsfEY.jpg&h=91766037&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n淨低七區我慢慢打　大家睇住先"},{"pid":"c6bc091dfd7c589746905fa861ebfecddafe71f1","tid":1849761,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:17:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=478517b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task2</span></span> 拎任務</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\nTask 2 好缺人，大家快啲去幫手！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，撳幾個掣都做唔到？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n1. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1222208859818860548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1222208859818860548&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=f836193b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1222208859818860548&h=9eb570a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1222208859818860548</a><br />\n2. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hawleymo/status/1222187690361311233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1222187690361311233&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jg2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=540ec80d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1222187690361311233&h=1c52d76d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hawleymo/status/1222187690361311233</a><br />\n3. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/tomtugendhat/status/1222141308631908355\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.c